      "raw_text": "Ben Tillet, one of the great Eng\nlish labor leaders and famous as\nan orator. will be heard in this\ncity some time this winter. Tillet\nis attending the meeting of the\nAmerican Federation of Labor as\na fraternal delegate from the Eng.\nlish trades unions. He will visit a\nnumber of cities in this country\nand will lecture on \"The World S\nLabor Movement\"\n\n\nA letter was received by the To-\ncal central body last night asking\nit's cooperation in making the lee\nture in this city success The\ncentral body endorsed the move\nment to have Mr.. Tillet speak in\nthis city."
    }
